# SERVER â€” DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENT
# ============================================================================
# Copy to: server/.env.development.local (recommended) OR server/.env.development
# Run with: npm run dev (after adding `dev` scripts below) OR `npm run dev:development`
# Never commit real secrets.
